 class=title> The New Hate....</span><hr size=1> The New Hate will be live on all servers this month and I am looking into getting stones to port groups there. I would love for us to get some of the new items that drop from the mini bosses and maybe even get epic items for those that need them from there also.  Heck, I would like to make it to the second floor even, maybe some of us Rangers can get planar armor then. When this gets planned fully I will be posting for sign up and then a go/no go policy on it. <br>
<br>
 This is going to be a bit of a rant now....<br>
<br>
 I have attended alot of raids with the guild and have gotten some nice gear on a few of them. I know that I cant get things in every raid we do and don't expect to. My rant is that untimely appearance of people going on raids. I was going to attend the last Seb raid and showed up in the nexus 15mins before the planned time. Guess what? I sat there in the nexus for 1 hour with only one other person there and 2 holding the camp. The person that was there with me came to the nexus with me.  Unfortunately, I went link dead due to power less in my house. So, I was unable to attend said raid. I found out though, there were a few people picked up for the raid that were not of our guild. This again is fine. I know that there will be times that we will need others. Atleast till our raid numbers become great enough to avoid asking others for help. OK, I think I may have said more than my fair share on this subject. /rant off...<br>
<br>
 Slyssf Silvermists 53 Pathfinder<br>
<br>
Looks like Saturday will be the first chance I have to get a hate raid going. Of course, this will be after Hollowing keys and hopefully we can get to Hate and find alot of the mini bosses up still and no one camping there. <br>
<br>
 OK.. to go I think we need the following:<br>
<br>
 2 tanks<br>
 2 clerics<br>
 1 chanter<br>
 2 wizards<br>
 2 backup healers<br>
 3 damage dealers <br>
<br>
 Then, after this anyone that wants to come along. I am thinking like 7pm CST for a starting time if that is to early for the minimum I have listed then we will try 9pm. I really want us to make a night of it here and get some decent drops for all. If we have people on that need epic items from here lets do all we can to get to them. As far as the SEoC I know I am not first on the list for it. Although, I do know these can be mq'ed for earthcaller. Lets just try to get all of them we can hehe. Warrior and Mage epic mobs can be taken if they are up and we have people there that need them. I am not sure about the items and havent taken time to read all the epic quest to know enough to talk much about them. I do know that the warrior epic mobs can be done by us. We just need to be very organized and take care of bussiness. I will post Go/No Go here friday night if noone wants to sign up. There will be NO GO if we dont get atleast:<br>
 2 cleric<br>
 1 chanter<br>
 2 wizards<br>
 1 MT <br>
<br>
 And dont even think of calling me a MT hehe. <!--EZCODE EMOTICON START :b --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/images/emoticons/tongue.gif ALT=":b"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END--> <br>
<br>
Ok thats all I have for this any suggestions will be very much appreciated. <br>
<br>
 Slyssf Silvermists 53(hopefully 54 before sat.) Pathfinder <br>
